import axios from 'axios'; import {useEffect} from 'react'; import TextField from '@material-ui/core/TextField'; import Button from '@material-ui/core/Button'; export default function ApplyTutor(props) { const {setDisplayNavbar, setUser} = props; setDisplayNavbar(true); useEffect(() => { const ac = new AbortController(); axios.get('/auth/isLoggedIn') .then(res => res.data) .catch(err => console.log(err)) .then(res => { if (res.isLoggedIn) { const user = res.user; setUser(user); } else { window.open('/', '_self'); } }) return () => { ac.abort(); } }, [setUser]); return
